Each tuple is of the form (note_title, text), where note_title often encapsulates the note type (i.e. section/subsection/display text of a theorem-like environment) along with the numbering and text is the text of the part. Sometimes title is just a number, which means that text is not of a \section or \subsection command and not of a theorem-like environment.




